## Introduction

In the sprawling, vibrant landscape of **Houston, Texas**, family is the cornerstone of our community. From the suburban reaches of Katy and Sugar Land to the historic neighborhoods of the Heights, the structure of a home profoundly influences the mental, emotional, and physical well-being of its inhabitants. While every family journey is unique and valid, decades of psychological research highlight the specific advantages found in a collaborative parenting environment.

